From e817e19844b53c51a518bcae3198f1a3f62fd46d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Wang Yi Jie <miwyj@mail.scut.edu.cn>
Date: Tue, 24 Mar 2026 13:33:46 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] rename AM_HOME/NEMU_HOME to JYD_AM_HOME/JYD_NEMU_HOME

Avoid env var conflicts with ysyx installation on the same machine.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
